name: TC_07_28_01 | Verify that user can edit template
description: Objective: To verify that a user can successfully edit an existing template by changing its name, message, role, and associated document, and ensure that the changes are reflected in the user interface and confirmed by appropriate toast messages.

Click "No,thanks" button on the One Time Special Offer Modal

Click the "Templates" item on the left SideMenu

Click the "Templates" item on the left SideMenu
